This paper discusses security and privacy issues in IoT platforms for smart homes, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also proposes a system for detecting and handling these issues, which involves symbolic execution and user interface design, indicating potential relevance to information retrieval (cs.IR), software engineering (cs.SE), control systems (cs.SY), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
